data.description: Step into this magnificent 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bath, 2-story Esperanza-style home. A long driveway provides ample parking for family and guests. Large yard, perfect for entertaining, gardening, or creating your private oasis. Step in to discover a harmonious balance of elegance and practicality, with tile flooring throughout the well-defined spaces. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring sleek appliances, and stylish cabinetry. The living room is a perfect ambiance for cozy evenings. Additionally, the home features a convenient half bath for guests on the main floor. Head upstairs to discover four bedrooms adorned with plush carpeting for added comfort. The main suite is a sanctuary of luxury, boasting a private en-suite bath. With a prime Mission location and these exceptional features, close to schools, expressway, shops, and dining, this home invites you to create lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own! Tour today!
